OL,3,CTory MP urges Scottish Parliament to
OL,4,C'up its game' and combat negativity
OL,6,FMr Mundell also claimed it "would be
OL,7,Fbeneficial" for joint committees,
OL,8,Finvolving both MPs and MSPs, to be
OL,9,Fconvened on areas that the Scottish
OL,10,Fand UK governments are jointly
OL,11,Fresponsible for, such as welfare.
OL,13,FThe Tory served as an MSP between 1999
OL,14,F` when the first Scottish Parliament
OL,15,Fwas elected ` and 2005, when he left
OL,16,FHolyrood after being voted in as the
OL,17,FMP for Dumfriesshire, Clydesdale and
OL,18,FTweeddale.
