OL,3,CTory MP urges Scottish Parliament to
OL,4,C'up its game' and combat negativity
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the 25th anniversary
OL,7,Fof Holyrood sitting for the first time
OL,8,Fon May 12, Mr Mundell recalled the
OL,9,F"sense of excitement, anticipation".
OL,11,FHe told the PA news agency: "It was a
OL,12,Fvery exciting time.
OL,14,F"There were very high expectations,
OL,15,Flooking back they were probably
OL,16,Funrealistic some expectations in that
OL,17,Fregard.
OL,19,F"But it was a period of optimism."
