OL,7,Fin Scotland in the 1997 general
OL,8,Felection, he told how the Scottish
OL,9,FParliament, established by Tony
OL,10,FBlair's government two years later,
OL,11,Fensured the party was again "part of
OL,12,Fthe mainstream in Scottish politics".
