OL,6,FHowever, he said a better than
OL,7,Fexpected result for his party in those
OL,8,Ffirst elections meant the 18
OL,9,FConservatives who were elected had
OL,10,F"cramped conditions" in the
OL,11,FParliament's initial temporary home,
OL,12,Fthe General Assembly of the Church of
OL,13,FScotland on the Royal Mile in
OL,14,FEdinburgh, as accommodation there had
OL,15,Fbeen planned on the basis of polling
OL,16,Fsuggesting there would only be nine
OL,17,FTory MSPs.
