OL,3,CTory MP urges Scottish Parliament to
OL,4,C'up its game' and combat negativity
OL,6,FBut he recalled the "greater sense of
OL,7,Fcamaraderie, particularly across the
OL,8,Fparties in those days", saying MSPs
OL,9,Ffrom opposing parties would often
OL,10,Fenjoy drinks or meals out together
OL,11,F"because everyone was in the same
OL,12,Fboat, all new together".
OL,14,FHe added that politics had "changed"
OL,15,Fand become more polarised since then,
OL,16,Fparticularly in the wake of the
OL,17,FScottish independence referendum in
OL,18,F2014.
