OL,3,CTory MP urges Scottish Parliament to
OL,4,C'up its game' and combat negativity
OL,6,FHolyrood committees ` which play a
OL,7,Fcrucial role in scrutinising
OL,8,Flegislation as the Scottish Parliament
OL,9,Fhas no upper chamber ` meanwhile were
OL,10,F"lauded as being very effective" in
OL,11,Fthe early days of devolution.
OL,13,FBut the Tory claimed the committees in
OL,14,Fthe Scottish Parliament had now
OL,15,F"become more political", adding that
OL,16,FHolyrood had "resisted the
OL,17,Fopportunity" to introduce elected
OL,18,Fcommittee chairs, as they have at
OL,19,FWestminster.
