OL,3,CTory MP urges Scottish Parliament to
OL,4,C'up its game' and combat negativity
OL,6,FAs a result of that he claimed "you
OL,7,Fget much stronger people as the chair
OL,8,Fof the committees" in the UK
OL,9,FParliament.
OL,11,FMr Mundell said: "At the point I left,
OL,12,Fpeople thought the committees here
OL,13,Fwere much more effective. Now I think
OL,14,Fthe committees at Westminster are more
OL,15,Feffective."
OL,17,FAdding that relations between the
OL,18,FScottish and UK parliaments are "still
OL,19,Ftoo ad-hoc" he suggested it "would be
OL,20,Fbeneficial to have some joint
OL,21,Fcommittees".
