OL,3,CTory MP urges Scottish Parliament to
OL,4,C'up its game' and combat negativity
OL,6,FBut he said the Parliament now had to
OL,7,Fwork to re-establish the "positivity"
OL,8,Fit enjoyed in the earlier days of
OL,9,Fdevolution.
OL,11,FThe Tory said: "My perception is there
OL,12,Fis much more negativity towards the
OL,13,FParliament than there was even a few
OL,14,Fyears ago.
OL,16,F"Particularly in areas like I
OL,17,Frepresent, the south of Scotland,
OL,18,Fwhere people feel marginalised.
