OL,3,CTory MP urges Scottish Parliament to
OL,4,C'up its game' and combat negativity
OL,6,F"When we started off I think there was
OL,7,Fa great hope it would be a Parliament
OL,8,Ffor the whole of Scotland, I think
OL,9,Fmany people feel that it is not a
OL,10,FParliament that is focused on the
OL,11,Fneeds of rural Scotland, for example."
OL,13,FThe MP continued: "The Parliament
OL,14,Fstill has the capacity to be a force
OL,15,Ffor good right across Scotland, but it
OL,16,Fdoes need to up its game and portray
OL,17,Fitself in that way.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@fO]uD@SOU
