OL,3,CTory MP urges Scottish Parliament to
OL,4,C'up its game' and combat negativity
OL,6,F"Part of that is by focusing on what
OL,7,Fare real people's priorities, not some
OL,8,Fof the distractions that have seemed
OL,9,Fto be its priority.
OL,11,F"I think there can't be any
OL,12,Fcomplacency. There has to be an
OL,13,Facceptance that there is a less
OL,14,Fpositive view of the Parliament than
OL,15,Fthere has been and it is incumbent on
OL,16,Fall the members, and the Scottish
OL,17,FGovernment, to turn that round."
